X^2+Y^2=Z^2+T^2+1
XZ−YT=A
x^2+y^2+z^2 = u^2+v^2
p^2+q^2+1 = s^2+t^2
p^2+q^2+r^2 = s^2+1
x^2-(d+1)y^2 = ±1
x^2-(d^2+1)y^2 = ±1
x1^2+x2^2+x3^2 = y1^2+y2^2+y3^2
(a-b)^2 + (c+d)^2 + (e-f)^2 = (a+b)^2 + (c-d)^2 + (e+f)^2
(a-b)^2 + (c+d)^2 + 4n = (a+b)^2 + (c-d)^2
{a,b,c} = {x+y, x-y, y^2}
x^2-(d+1)y^2 = n
